Description: This package provides tools for preprocessing MALDI mass spectrometry data, 
    detecting and cleaning peaks, removing contaminants such as keratin and trypsin, 
    generating spectrum plots, and optionally submitting peptide mass fingerprinting 
    data to Mascot, MS-Fit, and MS-Digest services for automated analysis.
